sub_title: Lecturer at Universidad Central del Ecuador
summary:
Global tourism professional with more than twelve years of experience in the hospitality sector.  Along the years my career has been nourished from intercultural tourism experiences, and life has given me the honor to share my knowledge with the future generations.

I like to inspire people to dare to live unique sensations, to refresh their day with a laugh; that through their travels they make dreams their own unforgettable memories, and that they break the hermetic schemes by discovering the world through their cameras.
